'''World Travel Exchange'''


URL = http://www.wtex.org


=Description=


"The World Travel Exchange (WTEx) offers its members the opportunity to "trade to travel". Launched in 2004, 173 trade exchanges have listed over 800 hotels and resorts globally. Their '''clients can travel the world and pay for it with accepted complementary currencies through this innovative exchange'''. WTEx will be utilizing the same cutting edge trade software as Current Innovations, providing inter-exchange opportunities in the future."


